quran[6{c,v,t}:
6,152,"aur yeh ke yateem ke maal ke qareeb nah jao magar aisay tareeqa se jo behtareen ho, yahan taq ke woh apne sun Rashd ko poanch jaye aur naap toal mein poora insaaf karo, hum har shakhs par zimma daari ka itna hi baar rakhtay hain jitna is ke imkaan mein hai, aur jab baat kaho insaaf ki kaho khuwa maamla apne rishta daar hi ka kyun nah ho, aur Allah ke ehad ko poora karo un baton ki hadaayat Allah ne tumhe ki hai shayad ke tum nasiyaat qubool karo"
6,153,"neez is ki hadaayat yeh hai ke yahi mera seedha rasta hai lehaza tum isi par chalo aur dosray raastoon par nah chalo ke woh is ke rastay se hata kar tumhe paragandah kar den ge yeh hai woh hadaayat jo tumahray rab ne tumhe ki hai, shayad ke tum kaj rawi se bachcho"
6,154,phir hum ne moose ko kitaab ataa ki thi jo bhalai ki rawish ikhtiyar karne walay ensaan par Nemat ki takmeel aur har zurori cheez ki tafseel aur sara sar hadaayat aur rehmat thi ( aur is liye bani Israel ko di gayi thi ke ) shayad log apne rab ki mulaqaat par imaan layein
6,155,"aur isi terhan yeh kitaab hum ne nazil ki hai, aik barket wali kitaab pas tum iss ki pairwi karo aur taqwa ki rawish ikhtiyar karo, baeed nahi ke tum par reham kya jaye"
6,156,"ab tum yeh nahi keh satke ke kitaab to hum se pehlay ke do garohoon ko di gayi thi, aur hum ko kuch khabar nah thi ke woh kya parhte parhatay thay"
6,157,"aur ab tum yeh bahana bhi nahi kar saktay ke agar hum par kitaab nazil ki gayi hoti to hum un se ziyada raast ro saabit hotay tumahray paas tumahray rab ki taraf se aik Daleel roshan aur hadaayat aur rehmat aa gayi hai, ab is se barh kar zalim kon hoga jo Allah ki ayaat kojhutla-ay aur un se mun moray jo log hamari ayaat se mun morty hain inhen is ro gardani ki Padaash mein hum bad tareen saza day kar rahen ge"
